channel.description: Hey, i was wondering if anyone had a copy of java sdk for mac that they can e-mail me. I have been all over the place, the oracle site has taken down all mac downloads from what i can see (if you find other wise you can pm me link and call me a loser). I have signed up for a dev team for one of my favorite servers and i need sdk to complete a task to get accepted. So it will be a huge help if anyone can get me a copy of java sdk for mac. if you can either send me link, or email me the file at xbox360manx7456@aim.com. :) ;) :D
